{"metadata": {"team_id": "strip", "topic_id": "1008", "run_id": "strip-opportunity", "task": "english"}, "responses": [{"text": "This report addresses: China's J-10 fighter jets", "citations": {}}, {"text": "Australia's commitment to pursue the acquisition of nuclear-power submarines under AUKUS was confirmed by Prime Minister Anthony Albanese alongside UK Prime Minister Rishi Sunak and US President Joe Biden in San Diego on Tuesday\n\nProfessor Hugh White (pictured) has slammed the AUKUS deal, saying it acts as a promise that Australia will follow the US into a future conflict against China\u00a0\n\n'This is a very serious transformation of the nature of our alliance with the United States,' professor White said in an interview recorded for the ANU's politics podcast Democracy Sausage.", "citations": {"461e91f6-8cd4-4753-9fc0-30319e78e1dc_203573455": 19.0}}, {"text": "Top defence expert warns Australia could be dragged into World War 3 with Beijing over its AUKUS deal - as alarming map shows Chinese missiles could hit two thirds of the country\n\n  \u2022 ANU professor Hugh White has slammed the AUKUS deal\n  \u2022 He says it's a promise Australia will follow the US into war\n  \u2022 Defence maps have revealed the range of China's missiles\n\nA top defence expert has slammed the AUKUS nuclear submarine deal saying it could lead to Australia being forced to follow the US into a war against\u00a0China.", "citations": {"461e91f6-8cd4-4753-9fc0-30319e78e1dc_203573455": 18.0}}, {"text": "This kind of interaction that promotes mutual respect, mutual benefit and win-win cooperation is not limited to the China-Australia economic and trade level, but is what the relationship between the two countries should always look like.", "citations": {"14d044e2-db98-4413-80d5-19f0469ce4c2_376396591": 11.0}}, {"text": "Home>>\n\nHope Australian PM's visit to China draws an uppercase \u2018J\u2019 for bilateral relations: Global Times editorial\n\nBy Global Times (Global Times) 15:47, November 05, 2023\n\nIllustration: Chen Xia/GT\n\nTo a certain extent, it can be said that Australian Prime Minister (PM) Anthony Albanese's visit to China is already half successful even before he arrives in Beijing.", "citations": {"14d044e2-db98-4413-80d5-19f0469ce4c2_376396591": 10.0}}, {"text": "Military publication Stars and Stripes described the P-8A as \u201ca multirole, twin-engine aircraft based on Boeing\u2019s 737 Next Generation airliner,\u201d adding, \u201cIts missions include intelligence, surveillance and reconnaissance, patrol, search and rescue and anti-submarine warfare.\u201d\n\nMORE ON CHINA GEOPOLITICS\n\nStars and Stripes added that the Taiwanese government stated the PLA\u2019s exercises in the region involved \u201cJ-10 and J-16 fighter jets, H-6 bombers, Y-8 EW transport jets, unmanned aerial vehicles and carrier-based aircraft.\u201d\n\nThe event led to some posturing between the PLA and the Navy.", "citations": {"d2e35ba6-2105-4403-b4f2-a1a4e21c84d8_493779786": 29.0}}, {"text": "The Navy\u2019s 7th Fleet defended the maneuver in a statement, \u201cBy operating within the Taiwan Strait in accordance with international law, the United States upholds the navigational rights and freedoms of all nations.\u201d\n\nWhile the PLA\u2019s Eastern Theatre Command posted on its WeChat account, \u201cTroops in the theatre are always on high alert and will resolutely defend national sovereignty and security as well as regional peace and stability,\u201d Reuters noted.", "citations": {"d2e35ba6-2105-4403-b4f2-a1a4e21c84d8_493779786": 18.0}}], "references": ["461e91f6-8cd4-4753-9fc0-30319e78e1dc_203573455", "14d044e2-db98-4413-80d5-19f0469ce4c2_376396591", "d2e35ba6-2105-4403-b4f2-a1a4e21c84d8_493779786"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "strip", "topic_id": "1009", "run_id": "strip-opportunity", "task": "english"}, "responses": [{"text": "This report addresses: Saharan Dust Storm Impact", "citations": {}}, {"text": "Timing of Saharan dust:\n\nMonday - Little changes will be in the forecast as heavier amounts of dust remain over the gulf coast.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 9.0}}, {"text": "The dust is a combination of sand and dust traveling from North Africa across the Atlantic that peaking in late June through mid-August.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 7.0}}, {"text": "Here are some things you may not know about Saharan dust:\n\nKEY TAKEAWAYS\n\n  \u2022 Millions of tons of dust are transported across the Atlantic every year\n  \u2022 Nutrient-rich Saharan dust plays a crucial role in the global ecosystem\n  \u2022 Dust suppresses hurricane development\n\nWHOLE LOTTA DUST!", "citations": {"847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659": 13.0}}, {"text": "Here are some things you may not know about Saharan dust\n\nDust from Africa moves across the Atlantic every year from late spring to early fall\n\nIt\u2019s a common visitor in the summer months: dust from the Saharan Desert.", "citations": {"847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659": 11.0}}, {"text": "Others think it is the metals or organics in the dust, and then some think it\u2019s the bacteria and fungi.\u201d\n\nThe Saharan dust cloud carries vast amounts of sand particles that transport bacteria and fungi.", "citations": {"958ae1ee-19d5-41c4-8e42-0583f3ed6841_957102541": 12.0}}, {"text": "Hidden passengers in Sahara dust\n\n\u201cWe all get allergies and potentially other more severe health effects when we breathe in dust, and it\u2019s not fully known as to what causes those allergies,\u201d said Dr.", "citations": {"958ae1ee-19d5-41c4-8e42-0583f3ed6841_957102541": 8.0}}], "references": ["5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364", "847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659", "958ae1ee-19d5-41c4-8e42-0583f3ed6841_957102541"]}
